==English==
===Etymology===
From [[w:Ejnar Hertzsprung|Ejnar Hertzsprung]] and [[w:Henry Norris Russell|Henry Norris Russell]], astronomers
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''Hertzsprung-Russell diagram'''
#{{star}}: a [[plot]] of the [[absolute magnitude]] of [[star]]s versus their [[colour]] (or [[surface]] [[temperature]]); shows the [[main sequence]] of stars plus the [[white dwarf]]s and [[red giant]]s

